column1: Skill
LEAD-A-FOU - Work within a small team
LEAD-B-FOU - Motivate and Influence a small team
LEAD-C-FOU - Devlop individuals within your team
ETHI-A-FOU - Conducts operations ethically
ETHI-B-FOU - Behaves ethically in barracks environment
CHAR-A-FOU - Reflect and adapt own behaviour
CHAR-B-FOU - Develop respectful working relationships
CULT-A-FOU - Display soldierly conduct
CULT-B-FOU - Performs basic individual and collective drill
CULT-C-FOU - Adhere to Military Discipline
TD-ID-A-FOU - Deliver training
TD-ID-B-FOU - Conduct Assessment
TD-PMF-A-FOU - Maintain Basic Physical Fitness
TD-PMF-B-FOU - Develop mental fitness
MA-ASO-A-FOU - Conduct basic personal administration
MA-RA-A-FOU - Use land materiel responsibily
MA-GA-A-FOU - Comply with Defence security requirements
MA-GA-B-FOU - Comply with Defence work, health and safety requirements
MA-GA-C-FOU - Comply with Unit Orders and Policy
MA-GA-D-FOU - Comply with Defence Social Media Requirements
MA-GA-E-FOU - Comply with Army Drug and Alcohol Policy
MA-GA-F-FOU - Produce a risk assessment

P-IP-A-FOU - Plan and deliver section level orders
THIS SKILL SHOULD MAP TO AN INTERMEDIATE PROFICIENCY WITH THE INCLUSION OF THE LEAD A SECTION LEVEL OPERATION

C-AW-A-FOU - Produce basic written documents
THIS LIKELY MAPS TO AN INTERMEDIATE COMPETENCY AROUND MANAGING PERSONNEL

FMS-UME-B-FOU - Employ SCE and PPE Tier 0 for field operations

FMS-ES-E-FOU - Operate the in-service Grenade
FMS-FC-A-FOU - Apply the principles of Army First Aid
FMS-FC-B-FOU - Survive in a CBRN Threat Environment
